Bootstrap: docker
From: PLACEHOLDER_IMAGE_REFERENCE

%post
    # Make /opt/conda writable for all users
    # This is essential for HPC environments where users lack sudo access
    chmod -R 777 /opt/conda
    chmod -R 777 /opt/R-cran/library
    echo "Made /opt/conda and /opt/R-cran/library writable for all users"

%labels
    Maintainer Fabian Rost

%help
    Apptainer/Singularity image from sequencing-docker-stacks.
    /opt/conda and /opt/R-cran/library are writable - install packages with: apptainer exec image.sif pip install <package>
    More info: https://github.com/huchlab/sequencing-docker-stacks
